/
/ IEEE 39-Bus New England System — Dynamic Data File
/ PSS/E Version 35+ compatible
/ Models assigned per machine:
/   GENROU  — round-rotor synchronous generator (all 10 machines)
/   EXST1   — static exciter / AVR (all 10 machines)
/   GGOV1   — turbine-governor, droop only KIMW=0 (all 10 machines)
/   IEEEST  — power system stabiliser (all 10 machines)
/
/ Parameter sources: Anderson & Fouad (2003), Pai (1989),
/   Kundur (1994), and published PSS/E benchmark studies.
/
/ ================================================================
/ FORMAT REMINDER (2-winding machine models):
/   BUS  'MODEL'  ID  p1  p2 ... pN  /
/ ================================================================
/
