/ GGOV1 — General Governor Model (Droop Only, KIMW=0)
/ Parameters (in order):
/   IGENRET  IREG   R    RSELECT  TPELEC  MAXERR  MINERR  KPGOV
/   KIGOV    KDGOV  TDGOV  VMAX   VMIN   TACT   KTURB   WFNL
/   TB       TC     TENG   TFLOAD KPLOAD KIMW   PMWSET  RDOWN   RUP
/
/ KIMW=0.0 throughout — pure droop, no AGC integral action
/ R=0.05 (5% droop) on all machines
/ VMAX reflects headroom: generators NOT at Pmax have VMAX < 1.0
/   allowing the governor to ramp up into reserve on frequency drop
/
